Positive Examples.input: i don't work i could take your shift i am a student
Positive Examples.explanation: In this dialogue someone is informing another person that they could take their shift. There is no happy, sad, or angry emotion in this text. So this is a good example.

Positive Examples.input: i'm not getting you loudlycryingfaceloudlycryingfaceloudlycryingface why are you crying because you are not making any sense

Negative Examples.input: i hate my boyfriend you got a boyfriend yes
Negative Examples.explanation: This text uses the word hate which is an angry emotion. The answer should have been angry not other. So this is a bad example.
